                </div>
                <p>
                    When he’s not describing himself in third person, Alec enjoys describing imaginary people in third
                    person instead. He loves dreaming up unique worlds, chatty characters, and has a soft spot for a
                    good play on words (and occasionally flicking through the Arts & Entertainment section for some good
                    words on plays).
                </p>
                <p>
                    By day, Alec is a software developer (giving him an unusual penchant for parentheses), by night he
                    sleeps, and by Jove is he excited to start work on the next book!
